{
  "stem": "7093.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in each room there where, I think, 32 beds or 36 beds-- not beds but bunks in two layers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we were-- and we were surrounded by grass and trees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a beautiful camp, really very, very friendly looking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were-- we could-- we were taken into the bathroom, which had hot and cold water, had plugs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were lots-- it was a row of white, clean, beautiful bowls, hot and cold water, a soap on each bowl, and a plug for each bowl.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we thought we were in paradise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were given somewhat some sort of meal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, we thought it's marvelous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now all our problems are over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And now we are going to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we are going to be fed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we are going to be looked after decently, and right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Anyway, some of my camp inmates-- I mean people like to have things, like to own things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they don't like it if somebody else owns it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So to make it sure that they owned it, they took off the plugs so that they had the plugs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they took away the soap that they had the soaps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so for others there was no plug and there was no soap.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And because that we were punished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they closed down the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when they occasionally opened it, then there was definitely no soap there, and definitely no plugs there, and definitely no hot water there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But this was how it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I mean, some people just have to have things, have to own things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so we could use the bathroom quite often, but not often enough.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And so I felt rather dirty.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
